Description:
Top Of The Class!
Located in the former Foy & Gibson 'New York on Oxford' Heritage listed building - this trendy warehouse apartment is impressive with its unique design and spacious floor plan. Opportunity presents to live in a modern apartment with real warehouse charm where key features including exposed brick, beams and high ceilings have been retained. It offers immediate comfort as well as additional scope to further enhance. Comprises three huge bedrooms, 2 with en-suites, plus study, open plan living, contemporary kitchen, powder room and European laundry. Other features include: heating, dishwasher, plenty of storage and secured car space.
Walking distance to all key amenities, including public transport, cafes and shops. Metres away from Smith, Gertrude, Brunswick & Victoria Streets with CBD, MCG & more just on the doorstep. Call Today!

Description:
Chic Apartment on City Fringe
Chic two bedroom apartment just a short stroll to popular Smith Street offers a fabulous opportunity for contemporary, urban living. Decorated in modern charcoal tones, the open plan interior comprises large lounge, two tone modern kitchen with space for dining, opening out to a tranquil, private courtyard. Two double bedrooms are fitted with generous robes and serviced by a bright central bathroom. In a boutique group of only eight, with secure intercom entry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, dual roller/Roman blinds throughout, easy off street parking and so close to the CBD, this apartment has everything for the astute urbanite.

Description:
An irresistibly cosmopolitan lifestyle
Embodying sparkling style, this brand new multi-level town residence has been superbly appointed with the latest fixtures and fittings to achieve a suave haven, just steps from exciting Smith Street.
Providing a balance of quiet sanctuaries and sun-soaked living, drive straight into the private single auto garage or park your bike in the spacious storage before heading upstairs to relax after a long day.
A substantial Caesarstone kitchen is sure to inspire the consummate chef with its long island bench and Ilve appliances, while guests enjoy the open-plan dining and living with north-facing deck and split system air-conditioning.
The top floor features a master bedroom with large deck, inspiring warehouse views, BIR, air-conditioner and a fully-tiled ensuite. The 2nd double bedroom with balcony is accompanied by a study/3rd bedroom and vogue bathroom. Boasts video intercom, laundry, water tank and provision for a lift.
In a boutique block of 5 and an easy walk into the city, live just seconds to vibrant cafes, restaurants and live entertainment venues and close to Fitzroy Gardens, MCG, and CBD.

Description:
Amazing Views & Huge Living Space this is sub penthouse living at its very best!
With views that will take your breath away, this exceptionally designed three bedroom, two bathroom prestigious apartment is now available and will not disappoint.
The apartment offers a state of the art Italian designed kitchen with huge natural stone bench tops, glass splashbacks, and Miele stainless steel appliances with gas cooktop, dishwasher and an abundance of storage. The living space is extremely generous in size, with floorboards and opens out to the balcony, which is perfect for entertaining. The master bedroom boasts a walk in robe and is great in size, while the second and third bedrooms are perfect for a guest room or home office. The apartment is serviced by the beautifully appointed Roger Sellers designed bathrooms. Also featuring ducted heating and cooling, and built in hard wood book shelves. With stunning views of the City. The building also features a state of the art gym and modern communal BBQ area.
Islington Silos is conveniently located within a short walk to Smith Street, Brunswick Street and the city, giving you the unique opportunity to wander down to your favourite, cafes, restaurants and iconic fashion stores. A stone's throw away from buses, trains and the Eastern Freeway. The apartment also comes with its own storage cage and parking for one car.
Internal area
142m²

PRICE REDUCTION - MOTIVATED VENDOR
A stunning contemporary vision from Bagnato Architects is concealed beyond a striking designer profile with this spacious and sophisticated townhouse staged over multiple light-filled levels. A premier position with sensational frontage in the hip and historic Foy & Gibson precinct, get the very best in a boutique block of only five with this stylish new city-fringe home discretely situated seconds to cafes, galleries, shops and trams with easy access to the Fitzroy Gardens, MCG and CBD. Features three double bedrooms with built-in robes (top-floor main with WIR, ensuite and huge north-facing terrace), two bathrooms, three alfresco areas including balcony, brilliant open-plan living and dining area, premium Ilve-equipped stone kitchen, laundry, store room, heating/cooling, video intercom, raintank plumbed to WCs and private remote-control garage (internal).

Description:
Charismatic Collingwood Character
The centrepiece with decorative parapet in a classic heritage row, this double-storey Victorian is an absolute charmer with a captivating period personality and compelling potential. An arched hallway, high ceiling roses and impressive open fireplaces lead the way to previously enhanced living spaces complemented by an upstairs outlook over the city skyline and a north-facing rear courtyard garden with ROW. This generous three bedroom home is as enchanting as it is enticing offering exciting scope to make it your own with some deft decoration or a designer touch in a fabulous location near increasingly popular Smith Street cafes, shops, parks and trams. Includes living room, casual dining area, modern kitchen, bright bathroom, laundry and storage.

Description:
EXCEPTIONAL DESIGN, MAGNIFICENTLY APPOINTED
Unit 1: This brand-new residence designed by acclaimed ITN Architects adds a whole new dimension to city-fringe luxury living. Built within the shell a former Deco-inspired factory and appointed to exemplary standards, it offers superbly zoned living over several levels and seamless flows to al fresco entertaining spaces. Filled with light, it includes a stunning living and dining room flowing to a wide balcony, bespoke kitchen (integrated quality appliances and stone benchtops), vast main BR/retreat with fitted dressing room, designer 3-zone ensuite and expansive terrace with CBD views, 2 further double BRs linked to an internal courtyard, and main bathroom/laundry. Including secure parking, this fine residence features large storage, tectonic oak floors, marble and quartz tiling, reverse-cycle a/c, video entry and cabling.

Description:
INSPIRED INNER-CITY WAREHOUSE LIVING!
A striking mix of industrial aesthetic and contemporary class, this townhouse-style apartment provides and amazing lifestyle opportunity right in the heart of cosmopolitan Collingwood. Located in the iconic Foy & Gibson precinct, the home's designer two-level interior boasts three big bedrooms and two stylish bathrooms, gourmet kitchen with Smeg/Miele appliances and vast open-plan living/dining with towering ceilings highlighting the building's exposed beams and trusses. Other stand-out features include split-system heating/cooling (both levels), polished hardwood floors, BIRs, big internal storage space, plus a private rooftop (third level) terrace, intercom/secure entry foyer and undercover parking space. Walk to Smith Street / Gertrude Street cafes, shops and trams, this is inner-city living at its brilliant best! Nelson Alexander Pty Ltd

Description:
HUGE FOY GIBSON WAREHOUSE CONVERSION
Situated within the desirable Foy Gibson precinct synonymous with warehouse living and moments to the ever-popular Smith and Brunswick Street lifestyle strips. This vast four-bedroom apartment (approx 230 m2) is distinguished by unique spatial variances, soaring barrel and lantern ceilings, elaborate turned-timber trusswork and metal industrial detail. Designed to capture maximum natural light, the apartment is set over several spectacular levels. Flowing from a room-sized reception area are a study, two bathrooms, a storage room, fitted laundry, and three bedrooms, one configured as a retreat with multi-fold doors to a private sitting area. A handsome timber staircase ascends to the vast living and dining zone, open to a kitchen with Ilve range, stainless steel benchtops and a butler's pantry. Above are a large mezzanine 4th bedroom with ensuite, open to a roof terrace with city views, and linked to a reading room set under the lantern ceiling of the original factory. This stunning residence features basement parking, airconditioning, intercom entry and quality appointments. See it and be captivated!

Description:
SPACIOUS APARTMENT WITH HUGE BALCONY & PERFECT LOCATION
Say hello to seriously stylish living, with this modern 3rd floor two bedroom apartment just off Smith Street. Big on space and featuring a trendy look and feel that maximises low-maintenance living. You'll love zipping out to `Proud Mary' over the road for a coffee or staying in and spreading out with masses of natural light and a free-flowing floor plan. Highly secure with intercom entry and a stylish facade,it includes a single car space and is ideal for savvy buyers or investors keen for a high quality opportunity.
the apartment has a fantastic sense of space with a study nook tucked to one side, and an expansive, bright open plan kitchen, living and dining area right out in front, with full-width, floor-to-ceiling windows comprising two sliding doors to a huge balcony - perfect for summer barbecues. The stone island bench is great for gathering friends around in the show-piece kitchen, plus there's an integrated dishwasher and stainless steel Bosch cook-top creating appeal. A balcony is the focus of the main bedroom, which also has walk-in robes to a chic ensuite with a large shower, while the second bedroom has mirrored built-in robes, heritage views and a nearby designer bathroom with a lab-style basin and stylish fittings.
Featuring a Euro laundry and split-system air-conditioner, this spotless apartment represents an outstanding lifestyle or investment opportunity with the CBD, Gertrude, Brunswick and Victoria St amenities, trams, cafes and entertainment in moments.
Jarryd Bow : 0430 519 639

Architect Designed Warehouse Apartment Over 2 Levels
An impressive heritage facade and amazing natural light will impress the owner occupier or investor seeking a timeless conversion with instant appeal. With a brilliant mix of polished concrete floor, stylish appointments and quality fittings the property comprises 2 double bedrooms with stunning central bathroom, open plan kitchen with stone benches, Euro appliances and gas cooktop, spacious living area, separate laundry, secure car park on title and storage cage. A private and secure base for you to embark on an exciting and cosmopolitan lifestyle situated within a stroll to transport, CBD, Smith Street, Gertrude Street and Brunswick Street shopping and cafes.

Description:
Single Fronted Character Victorian Terrace
In a wide street brimming with turn of the century Victoriana, this single fronted, well maintained, 2 bedroom brick terrace retains its original front fence and appealing facade highlighting a pocket size front garden and verandah trimmed with original iron lacework.
The classic c1900 interior has been lightened with well-placed skylights and extended at the rear to incorporate a spacious open plan kitchen/living area, timber lined bathroom and study/studio. The main bedroom is at the front of the home and the traditional arched hallway with a high ceiling leads to the 2nd bedroom (or living or dining room).
The compact kitchen features a timber bench and looks out to a lush fernery and the comfortable main living room embraces the organic warmth of exposed brick walls and slate flooring.
At the rear is a separate laundry and alfresco courtyard which alternatively offers car space accessed via a rear ROW. Features of this warm and welcoming home include gas space heater and gas hot water plus easy access to the Eastern Freeway, Victoria Park Station and bus to the CBD and Melbourne and La Trobe Universities.
- Character single fronted brick Victorian terrace
- Original lacework, leadlight front door and hallway arch
- 2 bedrooms, kitchen/living and study/studio
- Alfresco courtyard or car space via rear ROW
- Timber lined bathroom and separate laundry
- Close to Eastern Freeway, Victoria Park Station and city bus
Also visit the stand alone website at: www.109easeystreetcollingwood.com
Terms: 10% deposit, balance 60 - 115 days
Land: 141 sq m approx.
